The relevance of the company in the market, and in
society more broadly, has been further strengthened by
the changed geopolitical situation. The company is ready
to take on the increased responsibility and demand that
is expected in the years ahead.
Selskabet har fortsat vist resiliens i relation til Covid-19
pandemiens indvirken generelt og samtidig vist resiliens
overfor de udfordringer energipriser og forsyningslinjer
